# Backend base URL for the Mini App.
#
# Leave this EMPTY (recommended) to use the SAME ORIGIN as the page — Vite proxies
# /auth, /rooms and /ws to the backend. This is what you want both for local dev
# and behind a Telegram HTTPS tunnel.
#
# Do NOT set an http://localhost URL here for Telegram: the page is served over
# https (the tunnel), so an http request is blocked as mixed content and you'll
# see "Sign-in failed: Failed to fetch" with no request reaching the server.
VITE_API_URL=
